It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the *Software Engineer* position with *Symbotic*. I bring over three years of professional experience in distributed systems, real-time software, and backend engineering, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

